{"tid":755711,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]Kris Lau 被補","createTime":"2018-07-25T11:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T12:11:26.000Z","uid":59283,"like":636,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"224229fade4247537453218a7dd29219695c1549","tid":755711,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T11:59:35.000Z","msg":"現代教育英文科導師劉冠華涉貪被捕<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=314269&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D314269%26refer%3Dshare&d=O3GdHONW6uTLcbHmVovOSMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=fd8ce40c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D314269%26refer%3Dshare&h=40963851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=314269&amp;refer=share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】廉政公署起訴現代教育英文科導師劉冠華及一名考評局前評卷助理，兩人涉嫌貪污及非法收發文憑試的保密資料。<br />\n<br />\n43歲現代教育英文科導師劉冠華，被指去年4月17日至5月13日期間，以1000元報酬串謀19歲考評局時任評卷助理黃子軒，向他披露2017年文憑試英文科卷三聆聽及綜合能力部分的機密資料，兩人透過智能電話收發。<br />\n<br />\n黃子軒曾於現代教育修讀劉冠華的英文課程，兩人獲准保釋，星期五在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec89f91d73f10cf605a01d677129e577398e167","tid":755711,"uid":179571,"like":160,"dislike":2,"score":158,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:00:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f040b5964883719daf2a32bccc670f783b52c44","tid":755711,"uid":59283,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"quote":{"pid":"4ec89f91d73f10cf605a01d677129e577398e167","tid":755711,"uid":179571,"like":160,"dislike":2,"score":158,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:00:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:04:17.000Z","msg":"functional grandma"},{"pid":"30739722555b0940265a72351bb488306e21e66b","tid":755711,"uid":71140,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"914c711c046a0fbfb76c